&lt;p&gt;We are a mission focused, values driven company where each individual can contribute to building a stronger, more secure internet.&amp;nbsp; We offer a dynamic and flexible work environment with competitive benefits and the ability to grow your career.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;The Legal Operations Specialist provides high quality, efficient legal administrative support within the Verisign Law Department for the achievement of Company goals and objectives.&lt;/p&gt;
