&lt;li&gt;Works as a part of the Legal Operations team and provides direct support to the Manager, Legal Operations and other members of the Law Department team on an as-needed basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manages a variety of special projects as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Researches and follows up on legal issues as requested, including those of a sensitive or confidential nature.&amp;nbsp; Determines appropriate course of action, referral or response&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
