&lt;li&gt;Past work or internship experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Administrative/office experience supporting employees (including senior and executive level) in professional organizations (e.g., law or accounting firm) where attention to detail is required, highly preferred&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to occasionally move files/documents weighing up to 15lbs&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Occasional evening and weekend work required&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Skills&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High proficiency in Microsoft Office software suite (Word, Excel, PowerPoint, Outlook, etc.), Adobe products, Sharepoint, and other computer tools&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong written, verbal and interpersonal skills&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong organizational skills that reflect ability to perform and prioritize multiple tasks seamlessly with excellent attention to detail&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated proactive approaches to problem-solving skills with strong decision-making capability&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Demonstrated ability to achieve high performance goals and meet deadlines in a fast-paced environment&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven ability to handle confidential information with discretion, be adaptable to various competing demands, and demonstrate the highest level of customer/client service and response&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This position is based in our Reston, VA office and offers a hybrid work schedule.&lt;/p&gt;
